<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7760f3c5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7760f3c6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1998—Subsec. (b)(1). <ref href="/us/pl/105/277">Pub. L. 105–277</ref> substituted “Marsh-Billings-Rockefeller” for “Marsh-Billings”.</p>
</note>
